ção a favor, O QUE NOS FALTA!? LEVANTA NITERÓI!!! 43.333.<a href=\"http://www.danielmarquesdopv.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Construção-Civil.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-60\" title=\"Construção Civil\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.danielmarquesdopv.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Construção-Civil-300x187.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"187\" /></a>','A construção civil, o transporte e o desgoverno','','publish','open','open','','a-construcao-civil-o-transporte-e-o-desgoverno','','','2012-08-17 12:30:56','2012-08-17 12:30:56','',0,'http://www.danielmarquesdopv.com.br/?p=59',0,'post','',0),(64,1,'2016-03-16 15:21:43','2016-03-16 15:21:43','','home_hr_sectionbg4','','inherit','open','closed','','home_hr_sectionbg4','','','2016-03-16 15:21:43','2016-03-16 15:21:43','',0,'http://www.danielmarquesdopv.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/home_hr_sectionbg4-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(73,1,'2016-03-17 11:38:36','2016-03-17 11:38:36','<div class=\"column one-second\">[text* your-name placeholder \"Nome\"] </div>\r\n<div class=\"column one-second\">[email* your-email placeholder \"E-mail\"] </div>\r\n<div class=\"column one\">[text your-subject placeholder \"Assunto\"] </div>\r\n<div class=\"column one\">[textarea your-message x6 placeholder \"Mensagem\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"column one\">[submit \"Enviar mensagem\"]</div>\n[your-subject] - \"Formulário contato\"\n[your-name] <contato@danielmarquesdopv.com.br>\nNome: [your-name] <br>\r\nE-mail: [your-email] <br>\r\n<p>Mensagem</p>\r\n[your-message]\ncontato@danielmarquesdopv.com.br\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nBeHR - BeTheme \"[your-subject]\"\nBeHR - BeTheme <wordpress@themes.muffingroup.com>\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on BeHR - BeTheme (http://themes.muffingroup.com/be/hr)\n[your-email]\nReply-To: noreply@gmail.com\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try aga